title: Udemy -  Learn MeteorJS By Building 10 Real World Projects
description:
Meteor, or MeteorJS is an open-source real-time JavaScript web application framework[2] written using Nodejs. Meteor allows for rapid prototyping and produces cross-platform (web, Android, iOS) code.

With Meteor you can build your apps across web and mobile devices using Javascript. This open source framework is best for building powerful production grade apps in the shortest time possible. It provide libraries and tools to quickly take your idea to a live product serving across both web, android and ios devices.
